			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Personally, I would love the idea of getting rid of the boats and making the teleports right clickable to go from the wizzy location on each continent.  I would be able to go from North Karana to Luclin almost instantly.  I would be able to get a port to the wizzy spire or run if I needed to.  Then of course, once on the moon I could go to another continent relatively easy.  Sounds good to me.<BR>
<BR>
The other thing I would love to see is a melee useable bind and gate item.  As a pally, it takes forever to run from Lower Guk to North Freeport to bank and sell.  Getting a port in a dungeon is usually very difficult.  During a three hour period of playing, I typically spend at least an hour running between Lower Guk and North Freeport.<BR>
<BR>
If there was a relatively easy gate object, I could save tremendous time running to the bank.  I wouldn't care if it was a long delay on the casting.  Make it a 10 second delay if need be.  But it would certainly add to the fun of the game if I spent less time doing the boring bank runs.  <BR>

				</font>
			</td>

